blood. What do you expect me to do?

252
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:22,400
- Am I a gangster?
- No...

253
00:26:22,600 --> 00:26:26,800
That was Papa's neighbourhood.
Zasa runs it like a disgrace!

254
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:30,600
- That's the past, Connie.
- I earned that territory.

255
00:26:30,900 --> 00:26:34,600
The Commission gave it to me
and you approved.

256
00:26:34,900 --> 00:26:36,300
Yes.

257
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:40,900
I came for the party, not to ask for help.
I could kill this bastard.

258
00:26:41,300 --> 00:26:43,400
So kill him.

259
00:26:44,100 --> 00:26:47,000
What does all this have to do with me?

260
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:52,200
